<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Checklist Created - <%= @checklist.name %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .header {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #444;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }
        strong {
            color: #000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <%= @checklist.site&.name || "Site Management" %>
        </div>

        <h1>Hi <%= @user&.firstname || "User" %>,</h1>

        <p>A new Checklist has been created for your site (<strong>ID: <%= @checklist.id %></strong>). This notification was sent on <%= Time.current.strftime("%a, %b %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %>.</p>

        <p>Details:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Site: <strong><%= @checklist.site&.name || "N/A" %></strong></li>
            <li>Checklist Name: <strong><%= @checklist.name %></strong></li>
            <li>Frequency: <strong><%= @checklist.frequency&.humanize || "N/A" %></strong></li>
            <li>Start Date: <strong><%= @checklist.start_date&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") || "N/A" %></strong></li>
            <li>End Date: <strong><%= @checklist.end_date&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") || "N/A" %></strong></li>
            <li>Type: <strong><%= @checklist.ctype&.humanize || "N/A" %></strong></li>
        </ul>

        <p>We will notify you once there are updates to this checklist.</p>

        <p>Best Regards,<br>
        Team <%= @checklist.site&.name || "Management" %></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Powered by <strong>LOCKATED</strong></p>
            <p><em>Note: This is an auto generated email. Please do not reply.</em></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>